<div class='goals card card-block'>
	<h2>What would you like to do?</h2>
	<div class='action-forms'>
		<div class='customer-home-form'>
			<form id='goal-form' class='hidden'>
				<ul class="nav nav-tabs">
					<li class="active"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#home">Home</a></li>
					<li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu1">Retirement</a></li>
					<li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu2">House Ownership</a></li>
					<li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu3">Education</a></li>
					<li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#menu4">Car Ownership</a></li>
				</ul>

				<div class="tab-content">
					<div id="home" class="tab-pane fade in active">
						<h3>HOME</h3>
						<p>Navigate through the tabs to find the goal that applies to you.</p>
					</div>
					<div id="menu1" class="tab-pane fade">
						<h3>Retirement</h3>
						<p>I would like to retire in <select class="retirementYears"></select> years</p>
					</div>
					<div id="menu2" class="tab-pane fade">
						<h3>I'd like to buy a new Home</h3>
						<p></p>
					</div>
					<div id="menu3" class="tab-pane fade">
						<h3>Education</h3>
						<p></p>
					</div>
					<div id="menu4" class="tab-pane fade">
						<p>You may enter details about a car you would like to by or a by a monthly payment you can afford</p>
						<div id='car-dropdown'>
							<select name="Select" class='car-dropdown'>
									<option value=''>Select</option>
									<option value='1'>By Car Price</option>
									<option value='2'>By Monthly Payment</option>
								</select>
						</div>
						<div id='car-price-form-area' class='hidden'>
							<h3>I'd like to buy a New Car</h3>
							<form id="car-price-form" class='goal'>
								<label id='car-price-label' for='car-price'>How much is the car you would like to buy?</label>
								<input id='car-price' type='number' class='form-control car-input' name='car-price' placeholder='Enter amount' required/>

								<label for='loan-term'>What length do you expect your loan term to be?</label>
								<input id='loan-term' type='number' class='form-control' name='loan-term' placeholder='Enter length' required/>

								<label for='finance-rate'>What do you expect your finance rate to be?</label>
								<input id='finance-rate' type='number' class='form-control' name='finance-rate' placeholder='Enter amount' required/>

								<label for='down-payment'>How much do you expect your down payment to be?</label>
								<input id='down-payment' type='number' class='form-control' name='down-payment' placeholder='Enter amount' required/>

								<input type='submit' class="btn btn-signup btn-primary" id='car-submit' />
							</form>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class='action-button'>
		<button id='show-goal-form-button' type='button' class='btn btn-goal btn-primary'>Enter a financial goal</button>
	</div>
</div>